m electrodynamics\ncould be used in other types of mesoscopic circuits with many-body correlations\nand bring a promising platform to perform quantum simulation of fermion-boson\nproblems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Jul 2018 20:07:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-25"}
