 sequence data are not restricted to the residue pairs that are in direct\ncontact at the interface between the partner proteins.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Jul 2018 22:33:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 27 Oct 2018 21:54:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 13 Nov 2018 14:36:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-14"}
