ole of residual strains in such devices in relation to\nrecent experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Jul 2018 15:36:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Oct 2018 21:18:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-31"}
